Any information presented by Lensiary, including reminders, summaries, trends, predictions, environmental correlations or insights generated using Apple technologies, is provided for informational purposes only and should not be relied upon as medical advice.

Always consult a qualified optometrist, ophthalmologist or other healthcare professional regarding any concerns about your eyes, vision or contact lens use.

