# Personal Observations

Lensiary allows you to record information such as:

* Contact lens wear times
* Lens replacement schedules
* Comfort levels
* Dryness
* Irritation
* Redness
* Environmental conditions, including weather information retrieved from Apple's WeatherKit service

These records are intended to help you identify your own patterns over time.

The App does not determine the cause of symptoms or diagnose medical conditions.

Any apparent relationship between environmental conditions and your comfort should be considered observational only.

