# Apple Intelligence

Where available, Lensiary may use Apple Intelligence to provide summaries, insights or suggestions based on the information you choose to record.

These features are designed to help you better understand your own recorded data.

Apple Intelligence features are not intended to diagnose medical conditions, recommend treatments or replace professional clinical judgement.

